reviewText: Good little movie for 73 years old.
I like classic movies. The quality and audio was good! Because I have prime, I was able to see the movie without cost!
this copy was terrible. sound was bad and picture not clear. very very disappointed.

What a terrific horse story.  "Alfalfa" from the "Our Gang" kids plays a part.  A young boy takes his pet horse from his pal to horse racing with problems along the way.  Children and adults alike would enjoy this old movie.
